snippet.title: Super Grid Run Promo Video
snippet.description:
Promotional Video for Super Grid Run - A fast paced action runner game for Mobile and Desktop. Check it out at: http://www.supergridrun.com/

Simple One Touch Tap Controls, Global High Scores and Amazing Chiptune Music by Garry Lee - Sycamore Drive http://www.sycamoredrive.co.uk/

Inspired by Temple Run and Super Hexagon, Super Grid Run is Refresh Creations first commercial release and handily my first entry for onegameamonth.com a challenge to create 12 games in 2013. I hope I make it to the end!

I hope you enjoy the video and playing the game. Free Versions containing the first level will also be available for download.

More details including download links at: http://www.supergridrun.com/
